      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you, but the hotline stuff... it feels so fake. like they're just trying to patch up a ghost. what am i even supposed to patch up? the person everyone knew is gone. i'm just a hollow shell now. there's nothing left inside to actually help. it's like there's no point in trying to fix something that isn't even there anymore.",
